name: Funky Koala #3 | Christmas Time!
description:
This is my third edition of Funky Koala Pixel Art, Now i made a special christmas edition for you all. Now the funkykoala standing outside with the falling snow waiting for someone to accompany him celebrate the christmas eve. Will you accompany him?

Make this CHRISTMAS GIF as a CHRISTMAS GIFT

It's a little bit tricky to make this art, especially because of my wooden PC lol and my skill that not too pro. Day to day i'm usually write a program as a software engineer but in the other side i love to making art and i love Crypto and NFT. So forgive my skill of making art is absolutely so-so hehe. Merry Christmas Everyone, Love Y'all!
